#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.parley.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"Parley is a vocabulary trainer. It helps you to memorize your vocabulary, "
"for example when you are trying to learn a foreign language. It supports "
"many language specific features, but can be used for other learning tasks as "
"well. It uses the spaced repetition learning method, which makes learning "
"optimal. Vocabulary collections can be downloaded by \"Get Hot New Stuff\" "
"or created with the built-in editor."
msgstr ""

